SIMPLE: saying
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Saying
<hw>Say"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>That which is said; a
declaration; a statement, especially a proverbial one; an aphorism; a
proverb.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Many are the <qex>sayings</qex> of the wise,⟦br⟧
In ancient and in modern books enrolled.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><syn><b>Syn.</b> -- Declaration; speech; adage; maxim; aphorism;
apothegm; saw; proverb; byword.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sayman</ent>⟦br⟧
